FBIS4-36718 "drnes113_p_94005" FBIS-NES-94-113 Daily Report 12 Jun 1994 SOUTH ASIA Afghanistan Dostam Militia Commander, Men Join Islamic Army Dostam Militia Commander, Men Join Islamic Army LD1206172294 Kabul Radio Afghanistan Network in Dari 1600 GMT 12 Jun 94 LD1206172294 Kabul Radio Afghanistan Network Dari BFN [Text] Quoting a security source, a Bakhtar Information Agency correspondent reports that Commander Mohammad Zaman of the 195th Division of Dostam's militia and a number of his men joined the Mojahedin of the Islamic Army in Durah-e Hayratan, Mazar-e Sharif Province yesterday. The men who joined the Islamic Army pledged to carry out self-sacrifices for the defense of the territory of the Islamic State alongside Mojahedin and forces of the Islamic Army.
